# MODELOS A DESCARGAR  

## 🟣 FLUX SAFETENSOR
### DESCARGAR [FLUX DEV SAFETENSOR](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux1-dev/tree/main)

**Colocar en:**`ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models`  

---

## 🟣 Dual Clip Loader

###  DESCARGAR [t5xxl_xxxx.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/tree/main)  

**Colocar en:** `ComfyUI/models/clip`  

###   DESCARGAR [Clip L model](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/clip_l.safetensors?download=true)  

**Colocar en:** `ComfyUI/models/clip`

---

## 🟣 Load VAE

### DESCARGAR [ae.safetensor](https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell/resolve/main/ae.safetensors?download=true)  

📁 **Colocar en:** `ComfyUI/models/vae`

# PARA USAR MODELOS GGUF

Deben cambiar los nodos de carga del modelo
y del dual clip loader por el de tipo gguf

## Y descargar los modelos siguientes:

## ⚛️ Unet Loader (GGUF)

### DESCARGAR [Flux Dev Q8 GGUF](https://huggingface.co/YarvixPA/FLUX.1-Fill-dev-gguf/resolve/main/flux1-fill-dev-Q8_0.gguf?download=true)

**Colocar en:** `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models` 

O uno de menor tamaño de [ACA](https://huggingface.co/YarvixPA/FLUX.1-Fill-dev-gguf/tree/main)

## 🟣 Dual Clip Loader (GGUF)

###  DESCARGAR  [t5-v1_1-xxl-encoder-Q8_0.gguf](https://huggingface.co/city96/t5-v1_1-xxl-encoder-gguf/resolve/main/t5-v1_1-xxl-encoder-Q8_0.gguf?download=true)  

**Colocar en:** `ComfyUI/models/clip`  

### O uno de menor tamaño de [ACA](https://huggingface.co/city96/t5-v1_1-xxl-encoder-gguf/tree/main)
